 the treasury mr liddy served as interim chairman of the board and chief executive officer of american international group inc aig a global insurance and financial services holding company from september  until august  mr liddy served as chairman of the board of the allstate corporation a personal lines insurer from january  to april  and as its chief executive officer from january  to december  and as president and chief operating officer from august  to december  nominee qualifications mr liddy earned an undergraduate degree from catholic university and a masters of business administration from george washington university he brings to our board the benefits of his substantial experience as a senior executive and board member of several fortune  companies across a range of industries mr liddys extensive executive leadership experience at allstate and american international group enables him to provide our board with valuable insights on corporate strategy risk management corporate governance and many other issues facing large global enterprises additionally as a former chief financial officer of sears roebuck and co chair of the audit committee of goldman sachs and partner at clayton dubilier  rice llc mr liddy provides our board with significant knowledge and understanding of corporate finance capital markets and financial reporting and accounting matters which qualifies him to serve as a director of m source m company on    sign up for equilar atlas and view edward m liddys full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like edward m liddy more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in edward m liddys network and community follow changes in edward m liddys employment and moneyinmotion connect with edward m liddy through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example edward m liddy edward m liddys connections  sign up now 