 the board of directors previously he served for seven years in a series of positions with gd searle  co where his last post was senior vice president and chief financial officerliddy serves on the board of directors of m company and the goldman sachs group inc he is active in industry affairs serving on the boards of the insurance institute for highway safety and insurance information institute he is also a member of the financial services forum the business roundtable and catalyst  the leading nonprofit organization working to advance women in businessliddy is also involved in charitable and civic endeavors he is chairman of northwestern memorial healthcare and serves on the boards of boys  girls clubs of america northwestern university and the museum of science and industry he also serves on the civic committee of the commercial club and the executives club of chicagoa native of new brunswick new jersey liddy is a  graduate of catholic university of america and in  earned a masters degree in business administration from george washington university all american speakers is a speakers bureau and booking agency providing information on booking edward m liddy for speaking engagements personal appearances and corporate events contact an all american speakers bureau booking agent for more information on edward m liddy speaking fees availability speech topics and cost to hire for your next event tag cloud how to find favorite hire schedule famous entertainment celebrity recommended booking agency contact special event speaker bureaus corporate event keynote speaking edward m liddy appearance feesedward m liddy booking agency disclaimer edward m liddy booking agency celebrity appearance fees and availability contact a booking agent to check availability on edward m liddy and other top corporate entertainment exclusive buyers agent that books celebrities entertainers and speakers like edward m liddy for speaking engagements appearances and corporate events please note al